AWS EBS (Elastic Block STorage - Virtual storage )
-----------------------------------------------------
its block based storgae like hard disk .
Its used to run ec2 OS, store DB, weservers, file data etc
While creating EBS volume specify your availability zone, specify same zone same as you have EBS volume
Diff type of EBS TYpes
- General purpose - general most work load (web service) thsi si SSD - solid state drive 



















